# FCOP-derived map assets (.glb + textures) are NOT committed to this public repo
# (owner decision 2026-07-14: licence + size). To run ?render=mesh locally, copy
# them from the private RE-repo:
#   fcop-reverse-engineering/extracted/meshes/<Cont>/*  ->  public/models/<map-id>/
# (Cont->id: Conft=urban-jungle, Slim=proving-ground, Mp=la-cantina,
#  Joke=bug-hunt, Hk=hollywood-keys, Ovmp=venice-beach)
*
!.gitignore
